data.description: Introducing a stunning two-story, 5-bedroom, 3-bath home located at Chestnut Hills in Providence. This home boasts a 2-car garage, Kinetico water softener, RO system, and surround sound speakers. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, a custom backsplash, and recessed and pendant lighting. Throughout the home, you'll find coffee tone cabinets and shutters. Downstairs, enjoy tile flooring while the bedrooms offer carpeting and ceiling fans. The upstairs laundry room includes a front-load GE washer and dryer. The master bath showcases his and her sinks, a soaking tub, a separate shower, and a spacious walk-in closet. Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and turn this house into your dream home.
